{"questionId":"d5718376-6a71-41d6-aa0f-411bb7f3bb75_17","correctAnswer":"7","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Multiply the expressions","content":"Combine like terms: $$7x^4+10x^4-10x^4=(7+10-10)x^4=7x^4.$$"},{"title":"Identify b","content":"Comparing $7x^4=bx^4$ gives $b=7$. The answer is <strong>7</strong>."}]}